### Get all users
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users

### Get single user
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users/1

### Create new user
POST http://localhost:4000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Test User",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "age": 28,
    "role": "user",
    "address": "321 Test St"
}

### Update user
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Doe Updated",
    "email": "john.updated@example.com"
}

### Delete user
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/users/3

### Search users by name
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users/search?name=John

### Search users by role
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users/search?role=admin

### Get all products
GET http://localhost:4000/api/products

### Get single product
GET http://localhost:4000/api/products/1

### Create new product
POST http://localhost:4000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Tablet",
    "price": 299.99,
    "category": "Electronics",
    "stock": 75
}

### Get products by category
GET http://localhost:4000/api/products/category/Electronics
